These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, fanta, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, social-worker, videographer, nurse
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, ship
 1. the person driving the bike is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the photographer is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the social-worker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
 9. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
10. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Beverage   | sprite | iced-tea    | juice   | fanta    |
| Job           | videographer       | nurse   | social-worker   | photographer     |
| Transport     | bike       | airplane | ship  | bus      |

