.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, baccarat, dannemann
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, aquamarine, blue, grey
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who likes grey is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the chaman-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Cigar   | oliveros      | chaman       | dannemann | baccarat |
| Color           | blue       | grey    | aquamarine     | orange         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

