.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, tiparillo, game, chaman
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, bridge, domino
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
4 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, pony, turtle
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
11. the person playing bridge is the owner of the dog##1
12. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the game-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | chaman    | game      | tiparillo   | pall-mall |
| Game   | billiard | bridge | backgammon | domino  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Pet           | pony      | dog          | turtle | lizard  |

