.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, ebony, apricot, blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, pop, reggae
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, march, april
 1. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of metal and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | cola     | mirinda        | sprite      |
| Color           | ebony    | blue   | apricot | chestnut |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | metal    | country        | pop         |
| Birthday         | september    | march | april         | january    |

