.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, magic-tricks, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, zombie
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, scrabble, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, january, september
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Hobby         | camping | fishing    | magic-tricks | photography  |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | disaster   | zombie       | martial-arts |
| Game   | monopoly | chess        | backgammon       | scrabble      |
| Birthday     | december  | november | january   | september         |

