.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: grapes, papaya, peach, plum
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, classical, house, techno
House: townhouse, futuristic, gothic-revival, palace
 1. the fan of house is between the person drinking coffee and the person eating plum##2
 2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 3. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 5. the person eating plum is the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 8. the palace house is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 9. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
12. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | coffee             | cola       | water    | tea       |
| Food          | papaya             | peach      | plum     | grapes    |
| Music-Genre           | techno | house | pop     | classical |
| House   | futuristic           | gothic-revival | palace | townhouse |

