 1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
 2. the person who growstulip is between the owner of the bird and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 7. the german is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 9. the polish is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
13. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |    4     |
