.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: banana, lime, potato, radish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, june, april, july
City: marseilles, new-york, hamburg, paris
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| Birthday           | june | april        | november | july |
| City   | paris    | marseilles     | hamburg      | new-york        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel, house, trance
City: new-york, berlin, marseilles, hannover
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the fan of gospel is between the fan of house and the person traveling to hannover##2
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of house is the person traveling to berlin##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Music-Genre           | trance   | dubstep  | gospel        | house |
| City   | new-york     | hannover     | marseilles      | berlin   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

