.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lime, tomato, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, balloon-flower, sunflower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, game, cain
 1. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 2. the cain-smoker is the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
 7. the social-worker is the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the game-smoker is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
11. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
12. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry | tomato  | watermelon    | lime       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | balloon-flower   | sunflower  | tulip     |
| Cigar   | cain      | game    | blend        | montecristo |

 